Pisicevir Debian bootstrap package
==================================

This packaging exists to bootstrap and dogfood the Debian-to-PISI workflow.
The resulting .deb is intended to be inspected and converted by Pisicevir on
Devuan, then built and validated on PISI Linux.

Before repository submission, replace the placeholder Maintainer and Homepage
fields, confirm the project license, and require the full test suite to pass.
